{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"assign","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"showsUserLocation","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Setting this property to ","type":"text"},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" causes the map view to use the Core Location","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"framework to find the current location. As long as this property is ","type":"text"},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"map view continues to track the user’s location and update it periodically.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This property does not indicate whether the user’s position is actually visible"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"on the map, only whether the map view is allowed to display it. To determine"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"whether the user’s position is visible, use the "},{"code":"userLocationVisible","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The default value of this property is "},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Your app must specify a value for "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSLocationWhenInUseUsageDescription"},{"type":"text","text":" or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSLocationAlwaysUsageDescription"},{"type":"text","text":" in its "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Info.plist"},{"type":"text","text":" to satisfy the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"requirements of the underlying Core Location framework when enabling this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"property."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you implement a custom location manager, set the "},{"code":"locationManager","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" before","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"calling ","type":"text"},{"code":"showsUserLocation","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]}]}],"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)showsUserLocation","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"showsUserLocation","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"showsUserLocation","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"property","roleHeading":"Instance Property","title":"showsUserLocation","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L590","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"},"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/showsuserlocation"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/showsUserLocation","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"A Boolean value indicating whether the map may display the user location.","type":"text"}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control ove